Tesla Roadster
Price -₹ 300,00,000
Tesla Roadster was recently unveiled at Tesla Semi Truck launch event. The biggest surprise from US based electric car manufacturer, Roadster is a resurrected moniker that once came along the first Tesla car made around 2008. Extremely powerful and equally elegant, Roadster claims 0-97 kmph sprint time of just 1.9 seconds. This feat was never achieved before on a production car while drag racing specific models are the only vehicles that could go even quicker. 0-161 kmph takes just 4.2 seconds while top speed could go in excess of 402 kmph. Decent driving brings more than 1000 kilometers of driving range from the Roadster.
